IRELAND

ARE CONDUCTED THROUGH THE IRISH BRANCH OF TRAVELERS INSURANCE COMPANY LIMITED WHICH IS REGULATED BY THE INSURANCE SUPERVISION DEPARTMENTS OF THE CENTRAL BANK OF IRELAND (AS TO CONDUCT) AND

