LICENSES. IN EACH SUCH JURISDICTION, THE POLICIES WRITTEN BY TRAVELERS SYNDICATE MANAGEMENT LTD., AS PART OF LLOYD'S, ARE SUBJECT TO THE LAWS AND INSURANCE REGULATION OF THAT JURISDICTION.

