GROSS

AND NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS IN 2014 INCREASED BY 4% AND 5%, RESPECTIVELY, OVER 2013, PRIMARILY REFLECTING THE IMPACT OF THE ACQUISITION OF DOMINION. GROSS AND NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS IN

2013 BOTH INCREASED BY 1% OVER 2012. FACTORS CONTRIBUTING TO THE CHANGES IN GROSS AND NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS IN EACH SEGMENT IN 2014 AND 2013 AS COMPARED WITH THE RESPECTIVE PRIOR YEAR ARE DISCUSSED IN

MORE DETAIL IN THE SEGMENT DISCUSSIONS THAT FOLLOW.

RESULTS OF OPERATIONS BY SEGMENT

