IN

2014, GROSS AND NET AGENCY WRITTEN PREMIUMS WERE 4% AND 1% LOWER, RESPECTIVELY, THAN IN 2013. THE HIGHER RATE OF DECREASE IN GROSS WRITTEN PREMIUMS IN 2014 WAS PRIMARILY DRIVEN BY THE

