RESULT OF THE COMPANY'S NEW PRIVATE PASSENGER AUTOMOBILE PRODUCT, QUANTUM AUTO 2.0. IN 2013 IN THE AGENCY AUTOMOBILE LINE OF BUSINESS, NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS WERE 8% LOWER THAN IN 2012. BUSINESS

RETENTION RATES IN 2013 REMAINED STRONG BUT WERE LOWER THAN IN 2012, WHILE NEW BUSINESS PREMIUMS IN 2013 DECREASED FROM 2012. RENEWAL PREMIUM CHANGES IN 2013 REMAINED POSITIVE AND WERE HIGHER THAN IN

2012, PRIMARILY DRIVEN BY RENEWAL RATE CHANGES.

