TABLE OF CONTENTS

IN 2014, NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS IN THE AGENCY HOMEOWNERS AND OTHER LINE OF BUSINESS WERE 2% LOWER THAN 2013 AS A RESULT OF ONGOING UNDERWRITING ACTIONS TAKEN IN

