CONDITIONS. BUSINESS RETENTION RATES REMAINED STRONG IN 2014 AND WERE HIGHER THAN IN 2013. RENEWAL PREMIUM CHANGES IN 2014 REMAINED POSITIVE BUT WERE LOWER THAN IN 2013, PRIMARILY DUE TO LOWER RENEWAL

