INSTITUTIONS

THAT EXPIRES IN JUNE 2018. TERMS OF THE CREDIT AGREEMENT ARE DISCUSSED IN MORE DETAIL IN NOTE 8 OF NOTES TO THE COMPANY'S CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS.

