TRUST DEPOSIT AT DECEMBER 31, 2014 AND 2013, WHEREBY OWNED SECURITIES WITH A FAIR VALUE OF APPROXIMATELY $151 MILLION AND $181 MILLION, RESPECTIVELY, HELD BY AN INSURANCE

SUBSIDIARY WERE PLEDGED INTO A LLOYD'S TRUST ACCOUNT TO SUPPORT CAPITAL REQUIREMENTS FOR THE COMPANY'S OPERATIONS AT LLOYD'S.

