FINANCIAL INSTRUMENTS DISCLOSED, BUT NOT CARRIED, AT FAIR VALUE

THE COMPANY USES VARIOUS FINANCIAL INSTRUMENTS IN THE NORMAL COURSE OF ITS BUSINESS. THE COMPANY'S INSURANCE CONTRACTS ARE EXCLUDED

FROM FAIR VALUE OF FINANCIAL INSTRUMENTS ACCOUNTING GUIDANCE AND, THEREFORE, ARE NOT INCLUDED IN THE AMOUNTS DISCUSSED BELOW. THE FOLLOWING TABLES PRESENT THE CARRYING VALUE AND FAIR VALUE OF THE

