BEGINNING OF THE YEAR AND 38,738 AT THE END OF THE YEAR. THE DIVIDEND EQUIVALENT SHARES ARE SUBJECT TO THE SAME VESTING TERMS AS THE DEFERRED STOCK UNITS AND PERFORMANCE SHARES.

