BENEFIT PLANS, THE ESTIMATED NET ACTUARIAL LOSS THAT WILL BE RECLASSIFIED (AMORTIZED) FROM ACCUMULATED OTHER COMPREHENSIVE INCOME INTO NET INCOME AS PART OF NET PERIODIC BENEFIT COST OVER THE NEXT

FISCAL YEAR IS LESS THAN $1 MILLION, AND THE ESTIMATED PRIOR SERVICE BENEFIT TO BE AMORTIZED OVER THE NEXT FISCAL YEAR IS $3 MILLION.

