ASSUMPTIONS AND HEALTH CARE COST TREND RATE SENSITIVITY

THE FOLLOWING TABLE SUMMARIZES ASSUMPTIONS USED WITH REGARD TO THE COMPANY'S U.S. QUALIFIED DOMESTIC PENSION PLAN AND THE

POSTRETIREMENT BENEFIT PLANS.

