100% OF PERFORMANCE SHARES GRANTED), (III) 2,173,262 RESTRICTED STOCK UNITS, (IV) 242,643 DIRECTOR DEFERRED STOCK AWARDS AND DIVIDEND EQUIVALENTS ACCRUED THEREON AND (V) 92,187

